CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper March 11, 1961, pg. 18, reads: "Military Ball Guests - The Aerospace Education Seminar was held at the Hotel Hilton last Saturday night. Shown at the Military Ball are, left to right: Patricia Prattis, ROTC Maj. Rodney Coleman, Howard University, Washington, D. C.; Mae Louise Allen, and Cadet Alvin Scott, Howard University. The affair was presented by the Air Force Association and the Arnold Air Society. - Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Patricia Prattis (Jennings), Howard University ROTC student Rodney Coleman, Mae Louise Allen, and Howard University ROTC student Alvin Scott, posed on stairs for Military Ball during Aerospace Education Seminar, Hilton Hotel
